		<title>Excellent work culture contributes to the growth of Manila BPO industry</title>
		<link>https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/manila-bpo-industry.html</link>
				<comments>https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/manila-bpo-industry.html#respond</comments>
				<pubDate>Mon, 02 Apr 2012 10:13:06 +0000</pubDate>
